  Name:
    textVI: Timid
    textEN: Timid
  CharSprite: {fileID: 4909223577637351308, guid: 835da090a4feaa24a9bf418b76de31a0, type: 3}
  DialogueLines:
  - IsYou: 0
    textVI: "Ch\xE0o..."
    textEN: Hi...
    autoSkip: 0
  - IsYou: 0
    textVI: "Xin h\xE3y gi\xFAp t\xF4i, t\xF4i b\u1ECB l\u1EA1c v\xE0 kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt
      \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng ra..."
    textEN: Please help me find the way out, I got lost...
    autoSkip: 0
  - IsYou: 1
    textVI: "H\xE3y \u0111i th\u1EED v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa \u0111\xF4ng, t\xF4i v\u1EEBa
      t\u1EEB ph\xEDa \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE2y"
    textEN: Go to the east, I just got here from that direction.
    autoSkip: 0
  - IsYou: 0
    textVI: "Oh c\u1EA3m \u01A1n. "
    textEN: Oh thank you...
    autoSkip: 0
  - IsYou: 1
    textVI: "\u0110\u1EC3 c\u1EA3m \u01A1n t\xF4i s\u1EBD ch\u1EC9 b\u1EA1n \u0111i\u1EC1u
      m\xE0 t\xF4i h\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c trong l\xFAc b\u1ECB l\u1EA1c \u1EDF
      \u0111\xE2y"
    textEN: I wll show youi the thing that I learnt while I lost here.
    autoSkip: 0
  EndDialogue: 
